pageContext.claim: “I will say if the other side had won, if Hillary had won, you would instead of being up almost 50 percent since election, 5 million jobs plus, plus. Five million jobs, that's unthinkable.”
pageContext.analysis: There is no evidence this is the case, and a gain of 5 million jobs was not unthinkable. Job growth under Trump in the first two years was little different than Obama's last two years.
